// Deep Dives: John Sinclair & Perry Rhodan
// ------------------------------------------------------------------

+ [*] john sinclair [*]
- John Sinclair is the Chief Inspector (Ghost Hunter). He's in his mid-30s, blonde, wears a trench coat or suit, and is the "Knight in a Suit."\n\nThe Arsenal:\n- Silver Cross: Glows when evil is near, uses Latin prayer.\n- Beretta: Silver bullets, only shoots demons.\n- Sinclair-Team Ring: Communications.\n\nRules: Dry British humor, deeply responsible (must save civilians). He never smokes, never swears intensely, and never finds permanent love.

+ [*] perry rhodan [*]
- The Perry Rhodan Series Bible is a massive technical manual. Since 1961, pseudo-science must be perfectly consistent.\n\nThe Kugelraumer (Sphere Spaceship):\n- 800m diameter perfect sphere with a Ring Bead for sub-light engines.\n- Sub-Light is Impulstriebwerk; FTL is Linear-Antrieb.\n- Defenses: HÜB-Shield (glows blue, vents to hyperspace).\n- Offenses: Transform-Kanonen (teleports nuclear bombs inside enemy ships).\n- Authors must calculate real mathematical travel times to comply with series geography!

